Package: dell-milspec-tools
Version: 1.0.0-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Dell MIL-SPEC Tools Team <milspec@dell.com>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-psutil, bash (>= 4.4), coreutils, procps
Recommends: dell-milspec-dsmil-dkms, tpm2-accel-early-dkms, sudo
Suggests: dell-smbios-token, dmidecode
Installed-Size: 512
Homepage: https://github.com/dell/milspec-tools
Description: Management and monitoring tools for Dell MIL-SPEC platform
 Comprehensive userspace utilities for Dell Latitude 5450 MIL-SPEC platform.
 .
 This package provides:
  - Real-time monitoring dashboard for DSMIL device
  - Safe token testing utilities for SMBIOS tokens
  - Emergency stop mechanisms for safety
  - Resource monitoring and thermal protection
  - TPM2 hardware acceleration status tools
  - System health monitoring and alerts
 .
 The tools interact with kernel modules dell-milspec-dsmil-dkms and
 tpm2-accel-early-dkms to provide safe and monitored access to MIL-SPEC
 hardware features.
